I"{<p>“Citizens of Estimate Under, I ask for a moment of your day. Please heed my words, for there is a great trouble approaching.” Vious Obli stood behind the podium with a certain defiance she held throughout her career as leader of the great city. “I need every citizen to cooperate without question, there is not enough time explain the situation in detail.” Her voice boomed throughout every street corner leaving everyone silent. That is, almost everyone. Treme Ex quickly typed on his keyboard communicating with his coworkers while Vious Obli looked over his shoulder from the television broadcast glowing behind him.</p>
